    <description><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>按照数据流动顺序。</p></blockquote>
<h2 id="-历史记录附加">📜 历史记录附加</h2>
<h3 id="1-用户原始输入">1. 用户原始输入</h3>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-python" data-lang="python"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">res_stream</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">st</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">session_state</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">&#34;rag&#34;</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">chain</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">stream</span><span class="p">({</span><span class="s2">&#34;input&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">prompt</span><span class="p">},</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="s2">&#34;configurable&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="s2">&#34;session_id&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;user_001.json&#34;</span><span class="p">})</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><ol>
<li>参数：
<ul>
<li><code>propmt</code>：用户原始输入的字符串；</li>
<li><code>st.session_state[&quot;rag&quot;]</code>：<code>RagService</code>对象实例；</li>
<li><code>chain</code>：<code>rag.py</code>中的<code>RunnableWithMessageHistory</code>类型属性；</li>
<li><code>stream()</code>：LangChain 的<code>Runnable</code>接口的核心方法，返回<strong>生成器</strong>，用于流式传输出。</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>行为：这两个字典会<strong>先被传递给<code>rag.py</code>中的<code>conversation_chain</code></strong> 添加历史消息。</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="2-添加历史消息">2. 添加历史消息</h3>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-python" data-lang="python"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">conversation_chain</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">RunnableWithMessageHistory</span><span class="p">(</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="n">chain</span><span class="p">,</span>                          <span class="c1"># RAG 流程链路</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="n">get_history</span><span class="p">,</span>                    <span class="c1"># file_history_store.py 模块中定义的方法，期望一个 session_id</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="n">input_messages_key</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&#34;input&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>     <span class="c1"># 告诉 RunnableWithMessageHistory 哪个是用户原始输入</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="n">history_messages_key</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&#34;history&#34;</span>  <span class="c1"># 告诉 RunnableWithMessageHistory 把历史记录添加到哪个键</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">)</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>流程：</p>]]></description>
</item>
